channel.title: Worldone Is Coming Back (Testers Needed)
channel.description:
We are currently looking for people to test server find bugs and report them to us if you would like to test out and help us out, get to know the server before the release nows your chance. We are a 317 loading 602 witht 718 model header and some 718 maps We have most Bosses Nex Is still under going some work. Many different Custom items, we are also looking For model editors, preferably those who can animate capes and such for us.
[font=arial black]Message me or the owner on skype. @ilymage : The Owner/coder @zachary.ayd :Administrator[/font]
Pictures Will Be posted as we progress and get closer to the release. release date has not been decided quite yet, Thank you and hope to see some Testers in game. "I'm sorry If this is posted in the wrong area I was not sure"
